      <title>crontab 简单使用教程</title>
      <link href="/post/657465472/"/>
      <url>/post/657465472/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>cron 语法</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cron表达式 需要执行的命令或程序</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意： Linux cron最小调度时间为1分钟</p><p>cron定义说明: </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*    *    *    *    *</span><br><span class="line">-    -    -    -    -</span><br><span class="line">|    |    |    |    |</span><br><span class="line">|    |    |    |    +----- 星期中星期几 (0 - 6) (星期天 为0)</span><br><span class="line">|    |    |    +---------- 月份 (1 - 12) </span><br><span class="line">|    |    +--------------- 一个月中的第几天 (1 - 31)</span><br><span class="line">|    +-------------------- 小时 (0 - 23)</span><br><span class="line">+------------------------- 分钟 (0 - 59)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>**编辑cron任务: **</p><blockquote><p>/bin/bash 为Linux中shell脚本解析器，可将<code>/bin/bash /root/shell.sh</code>看作<code>java test</code></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 每秒钟执行一次 root目录下shell.sh脚本或程序</span></span><br><span class="line">* * * * * /bin/bash /root/shell.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>维护定时任务</strong></p><p>编辑cron任务，在控制台输入<code>crontab -e</code>命令编辑cron任务</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">crontab -e</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看crontab任务列表</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">crontab -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启cron任务</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service crond restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>任务列表</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 逗包ERP 7:00 重启</span></span><br><span class="line">0 7 * * * <span class="built_in">cd</span> /app/zserp/af/Tomcat2/bin &amp;&amp; /bin/bash starttm.sh &gt;&gt; /app/zserp/af/Tomcat2/bin/cron_logs.txt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 逗包调度 7:10 重启</span></span><br><span class="line">10 7 * * * <span class="built_in">cd</span> /app/zserp/af/Tomcat4/bin &amp;&amp; /bin/bash starttm.sh &gt;&gt; /app/zserp/af/Tomcat4/bin/cron_logs.txt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 果宝ERP 7:20 重启</span></span><br><span class="line">20 7 * * * <span class="built_in">cd</span> /app/zserp/Tomcat3/bin &amp;&amp; /bin/bash starttm.sh &gt;&gt; /app/zserp/Tomcat3/bin/cron_logs.txt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 果宝调度 7::30 重启</span></span><br><span class="line">30 7 * * * <span class="built_in">cd</span> /app/zserp/Tomcat8/bin &amp;&amp; /bin/bash starttm.sh &gt;&gt; /app/zserp/Tomcat8/bin/cron_logs.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">0 7 * * * cd /app/zserp/af/Tomcat2/bin &amp;&amp; /bin/bash starttm.sh &gt;&gt; /app/zserp/af/Tomcat2/bin/cron_logs.txt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">10 7 * * * cd /app/zserp/af/Tomcat4/bin &amp;&amp; /bin/bash starttm.sh &gt;&gt; /app/zserp/af/Tomcat4/bin/cron_logs.txt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">20 7 * * * cd /app/zserp/Tomcat3/bin &amp;&amp; /bin/bash starttm.sh &gt;&gt; /app/zserp/Tomcat3/bin/cron_logs.txt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">30 7 * * * cd /app/zserp/Tomcat8/bin &amp;&amp; /bin/bash starttm.sh &gt;&gt; /app/zserp/Tomcat8/bin/cron_logs.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
